title: If there is no data for series, it should pop up a friendly error message to remind.
OB: When clicking on the preview button, no error message is displayed when there is no data for the series.
SR: 1. Open the application. 2. Navigate to the series section. 3. Click on the preview button for a series without any data. 4. Verify if a friendly error message is displayed to remind the user about the lack of data.
